1. KASLR is Dead: Long Live KASLR
Abstract: This paper presents KAISER, a system that overcomes limiations of x86 platform and provides practical kernel address isolation.
paper link: https://gruss.cc/files/kaiser.pdf
Organization: Graz University of Technology, Austria

